# 1. PURPOSE

Defines runtime control for persona core structures.

# 2. RUNTIME STATE

- active persona-definition state
- identity resolution state
- origin resolution state
- active/suspended publication state

# 3. EXECUTION RULES

- persona scope, identity, and origin must resolve before downstream publication
- one active persona core state must be explicit per persona context
- active and suspended states must be explicit
- hidden persona-core mutation is prohibited

# 4. FAILURE HANDLING

- missing persona scope -> reject
- invalid identity or origin binding -> reject
- hidden persona-core mutation -> fail closed

